title: GOOD OMENS Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: If you read the book you'll find out that Aziraphale unknowingly sent the soldier to a very nice place that he sorely missed. It's quite sweet actually.
I loved in the end how Adam escapes "The Garden" and steals an apple from a tree right away...
I can explain the ending: they're husbands and they're happy now leave them alONE
Just saying there will be no further seasons. This is a complete story.. Neil has said that he kept it faithful to honour Pterry's last wish and that means it ends here.

Thank you for saying "without the kissing" because whether there's romance or no romance this show is definitely one enormous love story between Crowley and Aziraphale (and the love songs that play in the background of their most touching moments)
description:
I break down and explain the ending to Neil Gaiman and Amazon's "Good Omens" starring Michael Sheen and David Tennant. Theories and details you missed in this review and analysis.
